<HTML><HEAD><TITLE>USIA: U.S. Policy in Iraq -- News Analysis,
from USIA Washington File</TITLE></HEAD>
<BODY bgcolor=#ffffff><IMG SRC="usis2.jpg">
<CENTER><B><H2>News Analysis, Stories on Iraq<br>
</H2><br>Produced by the United States Information Agency</B><P>
<IMG SRC="footer.gif"></CENTER> 
