http://gopher.usia.gov:80/topical/rights/hrpamp/wehold.htm 198.80.36.82 19970213120737 text/html 40067
HTTP/1.0 200 OK
Date: Thu, 13 Feb 1997 12:07:42 GMT
Server: Apache/1.0.5
Content-type: text/html
Content-length: 39895
