<BLOCKQUOTE>
<P><B>Marshall Jones  : </B><BR> Assistant Director, Fish &amp;
Wildlife Service, US Co-Chair  
</P>
<P><B>William Nitze :</B><BR> Assistant Administrator,
Environmental Protection Agency, US Co-Chair 
</P>
<P><B>Eluid Martinez  :</B><BR> Commissioner, Bureau of
Reclamation, US Co-Chair 
</P>
<P><B>Will Martin :</B><BR>   Deputy Assistant Secretary, 
National Oceanographic &amp; Atmospheric Administration, US
Co-Chair
</P>
<P><B>Elbert Friday :</B><BR> Director, National Weather
Service, US Co-Chair 
</P></BLOCKQUOTE><IMG SRC="spacer.gif" WIDTH="1" HEIGHT="35">
