<DOCHDR>
http://gopher.usia.gov:80/regional/nea/gulfsec/irnsanc.htm 198.80.36.82 19970213123526 text/html 30777
HTTP/1.0 200 OK
Date: Thu, 13 Feb 1997 12:35:25 GMT
