editor, <i>Kant's Political Writings</i>. Cambridge, England:
Cambridge
University Press, 1970 (excerpt in Laqueur, <i>The Human Rights
Reader</i>).
<p>
Langley, Winston E., editor. <i>Human Rights: Sixty Major Global
