<P>Date:21/06/96  
<BR>Source: OFFICE OF THE EXECUTIVE DEPUTY PRESIDENT 
<BR>Title:APPOINTED AS MEMBERS OF THE <A NAME="HL0"></A><A
NAME="YOUTH"><STRONG>YOUTH</STRONG></A> <A NAME="COMMISSION"><STRONG>COMMISSION</STRONG></A>

<BR>-------------- 
<BR> 
<BR>OFFICE OF THE EXECUTIVE DEPUTY PRESIDENT: APPOINTED AS
MEMBERS OF THE <A NAME="YOUTH"><STRONG>YOUTH</STRONG></A>
<A NAME="COMMISSION"><STRONG>COMMISSION</STRONG></A>, 21 June
1996 
<BR> 
<BR> 
<BR>In terms of Section 4 of the National <A NAME="Youth"><STRONG>Youth</STRONG></A>
<A NAME="Commission"><STRONG>Commission</STRONG></A> Act, 1996
(Act 19 of 1996), the President, on the advice of the Ad Hoc
Joint Committee of Parliament on the <A NAME="Youth"><STRONG>Youth</STRONG></A>
<A NAME="Commission"><STRONG>Commission</STRONG></A>, has
formally appointed the following persons as members of the
<A NAME="Youth"><STRONG>Youth</STRONG></A>
<A NAME="Commission"><STRONG>Commission</STRONG></A> with
effect from 1 July 1996 for a period of five (5) years: 
<BR> 
<BR> (a) Full time members are: 
<BR> 
<BR>Ms Hlengiwe/Mahlengi Bhengu (Chairperson) Tell. 0825519157 /
011-3307425 
<BR>Ms Nomfundo Nozipho Mbuli (Deputy Chairperson) Tel.
011-8346865 / 011-4475701  
<BR>Mr Max van der Wath Tel. 012-3346050 / 012-3411024  
<BR>Mr Otto Bonginkosi Kunene Cell. 0825574294 / 031-3074962 
<BR>Mr Mpho Lekgoro Tel. 012-3738187 / 0824400454 
<BR> 
<BR> (b) Part time members are: 
<BR> 
<BR>Ms Nazeema Mohamed Tel. 011-6486394 / 012-3241066 
<BR>Mr Desmond Tsietsi Louw Tel. 011-9821036 / 011-9825826  
<BR>Mr Thabo Masebe Tel. 011-3336750 / 0825727301  
<BR>Adv. Richard Thabo Moloko Tel. 011-8023583 / 012-3285901 
<BR>Ms Rene Hendrina Susanna Jordan Tel. 016-333342 / 016-333333
x 2143 
<BR> 
<BR> (c) Appointees nominated by Provincial Premiers are: 
<BR> 
<BR>Western Cape - Mr Gavin Paulse 021-4036525-8  
<BR>Eastern Cape - Ms Yolisa Makasi 0401-91415  
<BR>KwaZulu - Ms Pinky Kunene 0331-942311/2 0358-202432/8 
