<HTML><HEAD>	<TITLE>Interpreting Services</TITLE></HEAD><BODY BGCOLOR="#FFFFFF"><CENTER><H1>Welcome to Deaconess Hospital Online</H1><A HREF="../overview/index.htm">OVIERVIEW</A>|<A HREF="../patient/index.htm">PATIENT INFORMATION</A>|<A HREF="../direct/index.htm">DIRECTORY</A>|<A HREF="../research/index.htm">RESEARCH</A><BR><A HREF="../educate/index.htm">EDUCATION</A>|<A HREF="../news/index.htm">NEWS &amp; CONFERENCES</A>|<A HREF="../employ/index.htm">EMPLOYMENT</A>|<A HREF="../new/index.htm">WHAT'S NEW</A></CENTER><H1>Patient Information</H1><A HREF="admit.htm">[BACK]</A> <A HREF="accommod.htm">[NEXT]</A><H2>Interpreting Services</H2><P>Interpreting services are available to inpatients and their families in most languages, including American Sign Language, at no charge. This service is available from 8 a.m. to 4:30 p.m. on weekdays. Translation services can be arranged in advance by calling Interpreting Services at 632-8498. For evening, weekend, emergency and all other requests, call the page operator at 632-8611 and ask the night nursing supervisor to arrange for interpreting service.<P><H5>Copyright 1996 Deaconess Hospital, All rights reserved.</H5></BODY></HTML>
