32-8911	<P>	Robert H. Bode, Jr., M.D.<BR>	<I>Vice Chairman</I><BR>	Phone: 632-8961	<P>	Robert L. Amrhein, M.D.<BR>	Phone: 632-8961	<P>	Donald W. Booker, M.D.<BR>	Phone: 632-8961	<P>	Edward Chen, M.D.<BR>	Phone: 632-8961	<P>	Susan M. Cid-Espanola, M.D.<BR>	Phone: 632-8961	<P>	Patrick J. Donahue, M.D.<BR>	Phone: 632-8961	<P>	James F. English, M.D.<BR>	Phone: 632-8961	<P>	Charles Falcone, M.D.<BR>	Phone: 632-8961	<P>	Robert Feliz, M.D.<BR>	Phone: 632-8961	<P>	Donald W. Foster, M.D.<BR>	Phone: 632-8961	<P>	James S. Gessner, M.D.<BR>	Phone: 632-8961	<P>	Stephen B. Jamison, M.D.<BR>	Phone: 632-8961	<P>	Istrati A. Kupeli, M.D.<BR>	Phone: 632-8961	<P>	Keith P. Lewis, M.D.<BR>	Phone: 632-8961	<P>	Robert P. Loebelenz, M.D.<BR>	Phone: 632-8961	<P>	Randall G. Mannella, M.D.<BR>	Phone: 632-8961	<P>	Ross J. Musumeci, M.D.<BR>	Phone: 632-8961	<P>	Edward K. Park, M.D.<BR>	Phone: 632-8961	<P>	Eric T. Pierce, M.D.<BR>	Phone: 632-8961	<P>	Tristan J. Psyhojos, M.D.<BR>	Phone: 632-8961	<P>	Thomas M. Redner, M.D.<BR>	Phone: 632-8961	<P>	Richard P. Shockley, M.D.<BR>	Phone: 632-8961	<P>	Michael Smalky, M.D.<BR>	Phone: 632-8961	<P>	Allison Smith, M.D.<BR>	Phone: 632-8961</BLOCKQUOTE><P><B>Pain Therapy Services</B><P><BLOCKQUOTE>	Thomas M. Redner, M.D.<BR>	<I>Director</I><BR>	Phone: 632-8961, 632-0458	<P>	Stephen Punzak, M.D.<BR>	Phone: 632-0458</BLOCKQUOTE><P><H5>Copyright 1996 Deaconess Hospital, All rights reserved.</H5></BODY></HTML>
