on, hyperlipidemia, weight management, insulin and non-insulin dependent diabetes, eating disorders, functional bowel disease, maldigestion and malabsorption, oncology and renal disease. Wellness visits are also available for general nutrition and fitness, as well as prevention of nutritional deficiencies. <P><H5>Copyright 1996 Deaconess Hospital, All rights reserved.</H5></BODY></HTML>
