Inpatient research protocols		<LI>Concurrent chemo and radiation		<LI>Unusual procedures	</UL>	<P>	<LI><B>Staff Education</B>	<P>	<UL>		<LI>Oncology nursing		<LI>Pain management		<LI>HIV symptom management	</UL></UL><P><H5>Copyright 1996 Deaconess Hospital, All rights reserved.</H5></BODY></HTML>
