	Phone: (617) 632-7705<BR>	meets every Thursday 8:00-9:00 a.m. in Kennedy 518</BLOCKQUOTE><P><B>Endocrine Section Seminar/Grand Rounds</B><BR><BLOCKQUOTE>	Director: Pamela Hartzband, M.D.<BR>	Phone: (617) 732-2501<BR>	meets Mondays and Thursdays 12:00-1:00 p.m. in Joslin Conference Room C</BLOCKQUOTE><P><B>Infectious Disease Clinical Conference/Grand Rounds</B><BR><BLOCKQUOTE>	Director: Adolf W. Karchmer, M.D.<BR>	Phone: (617) 632-0760<BR>	meets every Tuesday 12:00-1:00 p.m. in Kennedy G7</BLOCKQUOTE><P><B>Interhospital Infectious Disease Rounds (NEDH, BWH, MGH)</B><BR><BLOCKQUOTE>	Director: Adolf W. Karchmer, M.D.<BR>	Phone: (617) 632-0760<BR>	meets every Friday 8:00-9:00 a.m. (different hospital location every week)</BLOCKQUOTE><P><B>Pulmonary Medicine Conference</B><BR><BLOCKQUOTE>	Director: Paula Pinkston, M.D.<BR>	Phone: (617) 632-8251<BR>	meets every Thursday 12:15-1:15 p.m. in Palmer 108</BLOCKQUOTE><P><B>Rheumatology Clinical Conference</B><BR><BLOCKQUOTE>	Director: Steven Goldring, M.D.<BR>	Phone: (617) 632-8658<BR>	meets every Monday 8:30-9:30 a.m. in Lowry Medical Office Building, Suite 5A<BR>	(<B>please note:</B> this conference is restricted to department staff)</BLOCKQUOTE><P><B>Medical Grand Rounds -- Manchester (NH) VA Medical Center</B><BR><BLOCKQUOTE>	Director: Gerald Gehr, M.D.<BR>	Phone: (603) 624-4366, ext. 6247<BR>	meets every Friday 12:00-1:00 p.m. in the Training and Education Room, 1st floor, Main Hospital</BLOCKQUOTE><P><B>Pathology Grand Rounds</B><BR><BLOCKQUOTE>	Director: H. Thomas Aretz, M.D.<BR>	Phone: (617) 632-9010<BR>	meets every Monday 12:30-1:30 p.m.  This is an interhospital conference shared with Beth Israel and Brigham &amp; Women's Hospitals. Location changes every week.</BLOCKQUOTE><P><B>Weekly Pathology Teaching &amp; Research Conference</B><BR><BLOCKQUOTE>	Director: Harvey Goldman, M.D.<BR>	Phone: (617) 632-9010<BR>	meets every Wednesday 12:30-1:30 p.m. in Meissner 118 October through June</BLOCKQUOTE><P><B>Radiology Grand Rounds</B><BR><BLOCKQUOTE>	Director: H. Esterbrook Longmaid, III, M.D.<BR>	Phone: (617) 754-2526<BR>	meets irregularly, usually Wednesdays 12:00-1:00 p.m. in Clinical Center Radiology Conference Room 352</BLOCKQUOTE><P><B>Surgical Grand Rounds</B><BR><BLOCKQUOTE>	Director: Albert Bothe, Jr., M.D.<BR>	Phone: (617) 632-9236<BR>	meets every Wednesday 8:00-9:00 a.m. in Joslin Auditorium</BLOCKQUOTE><P><B>Surgical Joint Departmental Meeting</B><BR><BLOCKQUOTE>	Director: Albert Bothe, Jr., M.D.<BR>	Phone: (617) 632-9236<BR>	meets the second Saturday of every month 9:00-10:00 a.m. in Joslin Auditorium</BLOCKQUOTE><P><B>Tumor Conference</B><BR><BLOCKQUOTE>	Director: Keith Stuart, M.D.<BR>	Phone: (617) 632-8646<BR>	meets every Thursday 12:00-1:00 p.m. in the Meissner 118 Conference Room</BLOCKQUOTE><P><B>Plastic Surgery Conference</B><BR><BLOCKQUOTE>	Director: Francis Wolfort, M.D.<BR>	Phone: (617) 632-8039<BR>	meets every Wednesday 7:00-8:00 a.m. in the Cancer Research Institute (CRI) 2nd floor Conference Room</BLOCKQUOTE><P><B>Division of General Internal MedicineWednesday Conference Series</B><BR><BLOCKQUOTE>	Director: Eric Krakauer, M.D.<BR>	Phone: (617) 632-7064<BR>	meets every Wednesday 12:30-1:30 p.m. -- in Joslin Auditorium through June 26, 1996; thereafter in the Kennedy G2B Conference Room<BR>	(<B>Note:</B> lunch is served at this conference; come early if you're hungry!!)</BLOCKQUOTE><P><B>Cardiovascular &amp; Interventional Radiology M&amp;M/Quality Improvement Conference</B><BR><BLOCKQUOTE>	Director: George Hartnell, F.R.C.R., F.A.C.C.<BR>	Phone: (617) 754-2520<BR>	meets every Tuesday 7:15-8:15 a.m. in Clinical Center Radiology Conference Room 352</BLOCKQUOTE><P><B>Thoracic Oncology Program</B><BR><BLOCKQUOTE>	Director: Joseph LoCicero, III, M.D.<BR>	Phone: (617) 632-7403<BR>	meets every Tuesday 12:15-1:15 p.m. in the Clinical Center 2C Conference Room</BLOCKQUOTE><P><B>Combined Gastrointestinal Conference</B><BR><BLOCKQUOTE>	Director: R. Armour Forse<BR>	Phone: (617) 632-0948<BR>	meets every Thursday 7:00-8:00 a.m. in the Clinical Center Radiology Conference Room 352</BLOCKQUOTE><P><B>Non-Invasive Vascular Conference</B><BR><BLOCKQUOTE>	Director: Rola Saouaf, M.D.<BR>	Phone: (617) 754-2613<BR>	meets the last Friday of every month 7:00-8:00 a.m. in the Clinical Center Radiology Conference Room 352</BLOCKQUOTE><P><B>Henry Hardy Annual Bioethics Lecture</B><BR><BLOCKQUOTE>	Director: Regis de Silva, M.D.<BR>	Phone: (617) 632-9490<BR>	annual lecture given in January by a distinguished guest lecturer</BLOCKQUOTE><P><B>Neuroradiology Clinical/Pathological Correlation Conference</B><BR><BLOCKQUOTE>	Director: Edwin Fischer, M.D. &amp; Umberto DeGirolami, M.D.<BR>	meets every Wednesday 7:30-8:30 a.m. in Clinical Center 2 Conference Room</BLOCKQUOTE><P><B>Infectious Disease Conference -- Manchester (NH) VA Medical Center</B><BR><BLOCKQUOTE>	Director: Susan Hadley, M.D.<BR>	Phone: (617) 624-4366, ext. 6247<BR>	meets every 2nd and 4th Thursday, Room N-363, Main Hospital</BLOCKQUOTE><P><B>Clinical Topics In Diabetes (Joslin Diabetes Center)</B><BR><BLOCKQUOTE>	Director: Gordon Weir, M.D.<BR>	Phone: (617) 732-2501<BR>	meets every Thursday 8:00-9:00 a.m. in Joslin Conference Room C</BLOCKQUOTE><P><B>Longwood Area Diabetes/Metabolism Research Seminar Series (Joslin Diabetes Center)</B><BR><BLOCKQUOTE>	Director: Christopher Rhodes, M.D.<BR>	Phone: (617) 732-2501<BR>	meets every Thursday 4:00-5:00 p.m. in Joslin 3rd Floor Lecture Hall</BLOCKQUOTE><P><B>Pathway Health Network Managed Care Curriculum</B><BR><BLOCKQUOTE>	Director: Albert Bothe, Jr., M.D.<BR>	For more information or to register, please contact: Charlotte Warren, Pathway Health Network<BR>	Phone: (617) 632-0855</BLOCKQUOTE><P>The Managed Care Curriculum was established to provide educational opportunities for and to strengthen relationships among physicians within the Network.  Topics range from capitation and risk-sharing arrangements, changing relationships among physician groups, and ethical dilemmas posed by managed care, to the development of integrated health care systems.<P>The following <B>upcoming lectures</B> have been approved for 2.0 credit hours of Category 1 credit):<P><B>Wednesday, May 8, 1996 - 5:30-8:30 p.m.</B><BR>Doubletree Guest Suites, Waltham<BR>(6:45 p.m. light buffet dinner)<BR><B>"Surviving and Thriving Under Capitation: The Experience of the Friendly Hills Health Network (FHHN)" -- <I>Thomas R. Mayer, M.D., M.B.A., Senior Vice President, Medical Affairs, FHHN</I></B><P><B>Wednesday, June 12, 1996 - 5:30-8:30 p.m.</B><BR>Doubletree Guest Suites, Waltham<BR>(6:45 p.m. light buffet dinner)<BR><B>"Navigating Through Conflict in Turbulent Times: Renegotiating Skills for Physicians" -- <I>Leonard J. Marcus, Ph.D., Director for Health Care Negotiation and Conflict Resolution, Harvard School of Public Health</I></B><P><HR NOSHADE><P><A NAME="2"><H3>Deaconess Hospital<BR>AMA "Category 2" Approved Conferences</H3></A><P><B>Anesthesia Conference</B><BR><BLOCKQUOTE>	Director: Marissa Lazor, M.D.<BR>	Phone: (617) 754-2700<BR>	"peer review" session  which happens every fourth Wednesday 7:00-8:00 a.m. in Clinical Center 2nd floor Board Room. </BLOCKQUOTE><P><B>Cardiac Catheterization Conference</B><BR><BLOCKQUOTE>	Director: Samuel Shubrooks, Jr., M.D.<BR>	Phone: (617) 632-9204<BR>	meets every Thursday  4:30-5:30 p.m. in the Deaconess 3 Cardiology Conference Room  </BLOCKQUOTE><P><B>Neurology Case Conference</B><BR><BLOCKQUOTE>	Director: Edison Miyawaki, M.D.<BR>	Phone: (617) 632-8837<BR>	meets every Thursday 11:00-12:00 a.m. in Clinical Center 782 Conference Room</BLOCKQUOTE><P><B>GI/Liver Pathology Conference</B><BR><BLOCKQUOTE>	Director: Urmila Khettry, M.D.<BR>	Phone: (617) 632-9002<BR>	usually meets every 3rd Tuesday of the month, Sept through June,  in Meissner 118 Conference Room</BLOCKQUOTE><P><B>Pulmonary Radiology Conference</B><BR><BLOCKQUOTE>	Director: Philip Costello, M.D.<BR>	Phone: (617) 754-2567<BR>	meets every Thursday 8:00-9:00 a.m. in Clinical Center Radiology Conference Room 352</BLOCKQUOTE><P><B>Neuroradiology Conference</B><BR><BLOCKQUOTE>	Director: James Suojanen, M.D.<BR>	Phone: (617) 754-2514<BR>	meets every Wednesday 7:30-8:00 a.m. in Clinical Center Radiology Conference Room 352 </BLOCKQUOTE><P><B>Academic Thoracic Surgery Conference</B><BR><BLOCKQUOTE>	Director: Sidney Levitsky, M.D.<BR>	Phone: (617) 632-8386<BR>	meets every Friday 7:00-8:00 a.m. in Clinical Center 782 Classroom </BLOCKQUOTE><P><B>Vascular Surgery Conference</B><BR><BLOCKQUOTE>	Director: Frank LoGerfo, M.D.<BR>	Phone: (617) 632-9955<BR>	meets every Wednesday 7:00-8:00 a.m. in Clinical Center Radiology Conference Room 352 </BLOCKQUOTE><P><B>Otolaryngology Clinicopathological Case Conference</B><BR><BLOCKQUOTE>	Director: Renee Rossi, M.D.<BR>	Phone: (617) 632-8380<BR>	meets irregularly on Fridays 7:00-8:00 a.m. in Lowry Medical Office Building Suite 5C</BLOCKQUOTE><P><B>Weekly Psychiatric Clinical Conference</B><BR><BLOCKQUOTE>	Director: Carl Salzman, M.D.<BR>	Phone: (617) 632-8771<BR>	meets every Tuesday 8:00-9:00 am in the Palmer 5 Group Room</BLOCKQUOTE><P><H5>Copyright 1996 Deaconess Hospital, All rights reserved.</H5></BODY></HTML>
