P>	Christopher G. Gates, M.D.<BR>	<I>adult psychiatry, consultation-liaison psychiatry</I><BR>	Phone: 232-7609	<P>	Sarah Golden, Ph.D.<BR>	<I>psychotherapy, psychological evaluations</I><BR>	Phone: 632-8400	<P>	Bennett Gurian, M.D.<BR>	<I>geriatric psychiatry, consultation, psychopharmacology</I><BR>	Phone: 632-8400	<P>	Paul Hans, M.D.<BR>	<I>depression, panic disorders, geriatric psychiatry, psychiatric problems of the medically ill, psychopharmacology</I><BR>	Phone: 632-7720	<P>	J. Stephen Heisel, M.D.<BR>	<I>psychopharmacology, depression, general adult psychiatry</I><BR>	Phone: 632-8400	<P>	Alan M. Jacobson, M.D.<BR>	<I>psychiatric aspects of diabetes</I><BR>	Phone: 732-2594	<P>	Michael Kahn, M.D.<BR>	<I>inpatient psychiatry</I><BR>	Phone: 632-7790	<P>	John J. Mooney, M.D.<BR>	<I>adult psychiatry, affect disorders consultation, psychopharmacology</I><BR>	Phone: 632-8400	<P>	Martha Praught, M.D.<BR>	<I>psychopharmacology, depression, general adult psychiatry, geriatric psychiatry</I><BR>	Phone: 632-7720	<P>	Joy D. Riskin, M.D.<BR>	<I>inpatient and adult psychiatry</I><BR>	Phone: 632-8048	<P>	Barry Roth, M.D.<BR>	<I>adult psychiatry, consultation-liaison psychiatry</I><BR>	Phone: 734-3572	<P>	Jane T. Schwartz, M.D.<BR>	<I>inpatient and adult psychiatry</I><BR>	Phone: 632-7786	<P>	Russell G. Vasile, M.D.<BR>	<I>depression, anxiety disorders, psychopharmacology, affective disorders consultation</I><BR>	Phone: 632-8400	<P>	Cheryl Weinstein, Ph.D.<BR>	<I>neuropsychological evaluations, cognitive remediation, family interventions, adult ADD/LD evaluations</I><BR>	Phone: 632-8400</BLOCKQUOTE><P><B>Joslin Diabetes Center-Mental Health Unit</B><P><BLOCKQUOTE>	Alan M. Jacobson, M.D.<BR>	<I>Section Chief</I><BR>	Phone: 732-2594	<P>	Barbara Anderson, Ph.D.<BR>	Phone: 732-2594	<P>	Anne Butler, M.D.<BR>	Phone: 732-2594	<P>	John Zrebiec, L.I.C.S.W.<BR>	Phone: 732-2594</BLOCKQUOTE><P><H5>Copyright 1996 