<center><FONT SIZE=6><B>DISASTER RECOVERY 
PLAN </B></FONT>
<BR>
<BR>
<BR>
<BR>
<FONT SIZE=5><B>
</B></FONT>
<BR>
<BR>
<BR>
This is a small potion of the DRP, the remainder will be here early 1997.<BR>
You can make a copy and use it where you want.
<BR>
<BR>
<BR>
<FONT SIZE=3><B>Copyright 1986, 1987, 1988 by Systems Support Inc.
<BR>
All Rights Reserved</B></FONT>
<BR>
<BR>
<BR>
<BR>
<BR>
<BR>
<BR>
<BR>
<BR>
