<blockquote><p>
Disaster Recovery Journal presents Disaster Recovery World , World II and World III.  Few readers have been receiving Disaster Recovery Journal since its beginning.  Now with the World I, II and III you can get all the information you may have missed over the years, and now in an easy to use format that you will refer to often.<br>
