<font size=3>
<blockquote><p>

DISASTER RECOVERY FLOOD VIDEO
<p>
This chronological video features coverage of the Great Flood of 1993, the 1994 Georgia flooding, and the Johnstown dam break. Lesser known floods which have impacted businesses in the past are also showcased.
<p>
DISASTER RECOVERY EARTHQUAKE VIDEO
<p>
  See firsthand the damage earthquakes can do. These devastating natural disasters can strike anywhere at anytime with no warning - causing severe damage to businesses and residences alike. This chronological video features coverage of the the 1994 Northridge Earthquake, the 1989 San Francisco Earthquake, the Kobe Japan, Earthquake and many others throughout the world.
    <p>
 DISASTER RECOVERY VIDEO VOLUME II
<p>
  Disaster Recovery Journal has the New Disaster Recovery Video Volume II.  This video features fascinating footage of famous disasters such as the Great Flood of 1993, Hurricane Andrew, the San Francisco Earthquake, the Oakland Fires, the World Trade Center Bombing and the Kobe Earthquake.  Video footage is accompanied with music.
