(908) 758-2450, (800) 830-HELP<br>
<br>
Bellcores Network Integrity Services provides comprehensive prevention, containment, and disaster recover services for network outages and security intrusions. Our objective is to reduce the frequency, impact and duration of network outages by providing products and services that encompass every facet of Network Integrity. Using our 10-years of experience in network threats, hazards, and vulnerabilities, we can help you develop strategies to avoid business interruptions. Bellcore has the technical expertise and facilities to assist you with your network testing, disaster recovery, interoperability, network security, and reliability needs. Bellcores web site: http://www.bellcore.com.<br>
<br>
