CORT Furniture Rental<br>
Mark Koepsell<br>
4401 Fair Lakes Court<br>
Fairfax, VA  22033<br>
(703) 968-8561<br>
<br>
At Cort Furniture Rental, large scale and small scale disaster relief is an important part of our business. We work with corporations to establish parameters for setting up temporary offices if there is a disruption in key facilities. In a large scale disaster, employees often loose their homes as well as their offices. We can often work to help them establish temporary accommodations while we are setting up emergency office space. Cort Furniture Rental is able to locate and transport furniture in the most difficult situations because of our nationwide network of warehouses, and our clout with leading furniture manufacturers. Our relationships with leasing agents and property management firms allow Cort to assist in locating as well as furnishing temporary offices and homes.<br>
