<br>
Cylink Corporation manufactures wireless products for the global market in outdoor, high-speed data communications. Cylinks AirLink family of products is sold through value-added resellers and distributors in over 30 countries. Many counties do not require a license to operate them. Cylink offers: AirLink wireless modems for telephones and data rates up to 512 kbps, AirLink Bridge for full-duplex LAN inter-networking, AirLink T1/E1 for WAN, PBK, KTS and multiplexer applications. AirLink microwave radios reach up to 30 miles (50 km). They are ideal for "last mile" solutions where cable systems are expensive or right-of-way does not exist. <br>
