Disaster Services, Inc.<br>
Karla Torrey<br>
3030 Amwiler Road<br>
Atlanta, GA 30360<br>
(800) 669-1411, (770) 446-5300, fax (770) 446-5301<br>
<br>
Disaster Services, Inc. is a full service catastrophe restoration company. In a catastrophe situation, DSI is dedicated to one purpose: the timely, precise and thorough restoration of facilities and equipment to full productivity. Within 24 hours of notification, DSI is on the disaster site with fully equipped restoration specialists. Working around the clock, DSI sets the stage for maximum recovery. DSI will: 1) Assess the damage and take immediate steps to prevent further damage, 2) Establish the scope of damage and determine potential for successful restoration, 3) Identify and prioritize the repairs necessary to reduce business interruption and restore productivity, and 4) Implement specific restoration procedures. We offer a range of services including corrosion control, deodorization, soot and smoke removal, water extraction and dehumidification, contents and structure cleaning and electronic and manufacturing equipment restoration.<br>
