<br>
Earthquake Solutions offers a wide variety of educational and consulting services and also a large and unique range of survival products, including specialty earthquake fasteners. Both products and services can be customized. Courses emphasize mega-skills and include perspective on the human behavioral elements. Specialities include updated injury prevention techniques for earthquakes, decision criteria for the initial aftershock period, and issues regarding disasters and the young child. Solutions has a commitment to bringing sound earthquake education to everyone and thus will work with translators, and will discount fees for schools and non-profit organizations.<br>
