<br>
EMC offers high performance, continuous availability storage systems for IBM and PCM mainframes, AS400, and open systems. SRDF, Symmetrix Remote Data Facility, is a value-added software feature that provides a real-time image of your production system at a remote location. SRDF is an application independent and host CPU independent solution to real-time disaster recovery based on disk storage. SRDFs remote mirroring of critical business data allows you to recover your operations in minutes without loss of data. SRDF can also be used as a data mitigation tool for datacenter relocation and datacenter consolidations.<br>
