<font size=5><strong>Disaster Recovery Directory</strong><p>
<font size=3>
The Disaster Recovery Journal would like to announce the new updated version of the DISASTER RECOVERY DIRECTORY.  The Directory contains over 2000 vendors offering products related to the disaster recovery industry.  The printed version contains 5 listing including:  Categories, Alphabetical, Zip Code, Notes, and the Glossary.  This listing contains the most up-to-date disaster recovery products and services nationwide.  Hot-sites, cold-sites, consulting services, emergency equipment, and training facilities are a few examples of the detailed listing in the DIRECTORY.
<p>
